# ğŸ” **What is `Html5QrcodeScanner`?**

`Html5QrcodeScanner` is a **pre-built scanner UI** provided by the library **html5-qrcode**.

It automatically gives you:

âœ” Camera selection dropdown
âœ” Live camera preview
âœ” Scanning box
âœ” Automatic scanning loop
âœ” Built-in stop/start controls

You donâ€™t have to build UI manually â€” this class creates everything for you.

